they've done or what's happened.

545
00:52:52,519 --> 00:52:55,750
- Too self-absorbed that they...
- Self-absorbed?!

546
00:52:55,839 --> 00:52:58,558
That doesn't apply
to Annie, all right?

547
00:52:59,839 --> 00:53:03,388
No, it doesn't.
Suicides are different.

548
00:53:03,479 --> 00:53:07,791
They don't go to hell because
they're immoral or selfish.

549
00:53:07,879 --> 00:53:12,714
There's a natural order
to our journey.

550
00:53:12,799 --> 00:53:15,154
Annie has violated that.

551
00:53:15,239 --> 00:53:17,799
She won't face it.

552
00:53:17,879 --> 00:53:22,669
She won't realise,
accept what she's done.

553
00:53:22,759 --> 00:53:25,353
