is your life gone wrong.

556
00:53:50,919 --> 00:53:55,117
I'm her soul mate.
I can find her.

557
00:54:02,079 --> 00:54:06,948
- You don't understand how...
- It's not about understanding!

558
00:54:07,039 --> 00:54:09,394
It's about not giving up.

559
00:54:11,239 --> 00:54:14,470
You said there are no rules.
And the tree?

560
00:54:14,559 --> 00:54:19,349
